headline: Collins Aerospace approved to begin Full Rate Production of MAPS Gen II system
summary: Collins Aerospace, an RTX (NYSE: RTX) business, has received approval for Full Rate Production of the Mounted Assured Positioning, Navigation and Timing (PNT) Generation II system (MAPS GEN II).
